- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper's focus on LSTM networks and their optimization suggests that it belongs to this sub-category. 
- cs.EM (Emerging Technologies): The paper addresses the challenge of deploying computationally demanding LSTMs in emerging latency-sensitive applications, which suggests that it belongs to this sub-category.
